<p class="BubbleTitleSub">LandWarNet Remains a Top Modernization Priority</p>
<p>By Mr Stephen Murray, Requirements Integration Directorate (RID), LandWarNet Division (LWND), June 20, 2014</p>
<p>The Network remains one of the Army's top modernization priorities. Army forces require a coherent and integrated network capability to move information seamlessly under universal conditions and support all phases of Joint operations.</p>
